data.description: Buyer financing fell through and we are back on the market with a brand new roof & sump pump. Move in ready, located in the heart of Frederick's sought-after Wyndham Hill neighborhood, this pristine family home, built in 2019, showcases Colorado living at its best. With generous windows inviting ample sunlight, the upper-level offers captivating views that complement the home's 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Inside, you'll find a versatile den/office, high ceilings, and a practical attached two-car garage. The private backyard is a tranquil space, awaiting your personal touch.Enjoy a friendly and welcoming community, close proximity to parks, hiking routes, and biking trails. Frederick's strategic location ensures Denver, Fort Collins, Boulder, Louisville, and Lafayette are all within easy reach. This is a wonderful opportunity for comfortable living in one of the most cherished neighborhoods.
